WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 10=

00:01:41.850 --> 00:01:42.690 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:01:42.820 --> 00:01:44.820 line:80%
you must know about Yin Dai
stealing the credit.

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:46.730 line:80%
Why did you never tell me?

00:01:46.730 --> 00:01:47.896 line:80%
What good would it have done?

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:49.980 line:80%
So many people saw it.

00:01:50.370 --> 00:01:51.930 line:80%
Who ever spoke a word of justice?

00:01:52.010 --> 00:01:53.460 line:80%
But with my mother's temperament,

00:01:54.620 --> 00:01:55.820 line:80%
how could she endure it?

00:01:56.700 --> 00:01:58.290 line:80%
Your mother was furious at first.

00:01:58.780 --> 00:01:59.780 line:80%
But think about it.

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:01.650 line:80%
Your aunt was gravely injured

00:02:01.900 --> 00:02:03.260 line:80%
and didn't want to be disturbed.

00:02:03.650 --> 00:02:04.490 line:80%
Moreover...

00:02:05.540 --> 00:02:06.646 line:80%
My mother had anticipated

00:02:06.657 --> 00:02:08.290 line:80%
that the demonic sect
would seek revenge?

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:10.100 line:80%
Though Nie Hengcheng was killed,

00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:13.220 line:80%
his disciples were vicious and powerful.

00:02:14.020 --> 00:02:15.780 line:80%
Yin Dai took the credit,

00:02:16.140 --> 00:02:18.100 line:80%
so he naturally had to bear
their retaliation.

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:21.900 line:80%
So,

00:02:22.420 --> 00:02:23.260 line:80%
was Siqi Sect

00:02:23.620 --> 00:02:24.980 line:80%
massacred by the demonic sect

00:02:25.750 --> 00:02:26.980 line:80%
because of this?

00:02:27.340 --> 00:02:28.180 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:28.660 --> 00:02:29.940 line:80%
Yang Yi died an untimely death

00:02:30.060 --> 00:02:30.980 line:80%
in that massacre.

00:02:31.340 --> 00:02:33.100 line:80%
Only Yang Heying was left.

00:02:33.460 --> 00:02:34.860 line:80%
The Yang clan then declined.

00:02:35.820 --> 00:02:36.853 line:80%
All matters in this world

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:38.580 line:80%
are but reaping what one has sown.

00:02:40.260 --> 00:02:41.660 line:80%
Cause and effect cycle endlessly;

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:43.180 line:80%
retribution never fails.

00:02:43.540 --> 00:02:44.380 line:80%
Master.

00:02:46.260 --> 00:02:47.100 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:50.260 --> 00:02:51.100 line:80%
Xiuming.

00:02:54.460 --> 00:02:56.226 line:80%
The medicine for you
has just been prepared.

00:02:56.420 --> 00:02:57.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:57.176 --> 00:02:58.156 line:80%
take it to your master.

00:02:58.260 --> 00:02:59.100 line:80%
Alright.

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:01.940 line:80%
Thank you, Xiuming.

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:07.860 line:80%
Master.

00:03:11.620 --> 00:03:12.460 line:80%
Yunke,

00:03:12.700 --> 00:03:13.860 line:80%
where do you plan

00:03:14.020 --> 00:03:14.940 line:80%
to bury Qiu?

00:03:17.140 --> 00:03:18.900 line:80%
After all, we were fellow disciples.

00:03:19.300 --> 00:03:20.140 line:80%
I think

00:03:20.740 --> 00:03:21.580 line:80%
we should put him

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:23.740 line:80%
in the ancestral hall of Qingque Sect.

00:03:24.340 --> 00:03:25.640 line:80%
The Yin family's ancestral hall?

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:28.900 line:80%
Master,

00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:32.260 line:80%
Uncle Qiu would rather die
than turn back.

00:03:32.740 --> 00:03:33.580 line:80%
Perhaps

00:03:34.620 --> 00:03:36.453 line:80%
he wouldn't wish
to enter the ancestral hall.

00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:39.860 line:80%
Zhao is making a point.

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:41.700 line:80%
Then I'll find

00:03:42.740 --> 00:03:43.860 line:80%
another place for him.

00:03:45.100 --> 00:03:45.940 line:80%
By the way, Zhao,

00:03:46.820 --> 00:03:47.660 line:80%
that day,

00:03:47.820 --> 00:03:49.140 line:80%
when you fought that villain,

00:03:49.220 --> 00:03:50.460 line:80%
did you see his appearance?

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:52.660 line:80%
From head to toe,

00:03:53.260 --> 00:03:54.200 line:80%
he was tightly covered.

00:04:01.180 --> 00:04:02.420 line:80%
But I felt

00:04:03.326 --> 00:04:04.552 line:80%
his bearing was extraordinary.

00:04:05.420 --> 00:04:06.740 line:80%
Extraordinary bearing?

00:04:10.420 --> 00:04:13.100 line:80%
(Chuitian Dock)

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:13.940 line:80%
This saliva

00:04:14.060 --> 00:04:15.380 line:80%
is so miraculous.

00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:17.940 line:80%
I'll go fetch some more for you.

00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:19.140 line:80%
No need.

00:04:19.300 --> 00:04:21.610 line:80%
Uncle Lei said the saliva
can warm the meridians,

00:04:21.820 --> 00:04:23.100 line:80%
but it can only help me recovery

00:04:23.300 --> 00:04:24.140 line:80%
to this point.

00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:27.340 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:28.260 --> 00:04:29.540 line:80%
Why did Qian Xueshen

00:04:30.180 --> 00:04:32.180 line:80%
hand over the saliva once you left?

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:35.520 line:80%
He must be touched

00:04:35.840 --> 00:04:36.970 line:80%
by my sincerity.

00:04:38.100 --> 00:04:38.940 line:80%
And then

00:04:40.100 --> 00:04:41.380 line:80%
he died from poison?

00:04:42.060 --> 00:04:43.010 line:80%
The demonic sect

00:04:43.020 --> 00:04:44.620 line:80%
had long planted poison in him.

00:04:44.980 --> 00:04:46.020 line:80%
By the time I arrived,

00:04:46.031 --> 00:04:47.000 line:80%
it was already too late.

00:04:48.660 --> 00:04:49.500 line:80%
Alas.

00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:53.020 line:80%
Qian Xueshen is gone.

00:04:54.260 --> 00:04:55.100 line:80%
Then,

00:04:55.220 --> 00:04:56.180 line:80%
what about Chang?

00:04:57.060 --> 00:04:58.180 line:80%
Did you meet him?

00:04:58.420 --> 00:04:59.260 line:80%
Did he help?

00:05:00.460 --> 00:05:01.300 line:80%
No.

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:02.220 line:80%
I didn't see him.

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:03.740 line:80%
No one helped me.

00:05:04.100 --> 00:05:05.060 line:80%
Who knows where he went?

00:05:07.460 --> 00:05:08.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:11.740 line:80%
you really didn't go
to the snow mountains?

00:05:12.060 --> 00:05:12.900 line:80%
Of course, I didn't.

00:05:14.020 --> 00:05:16.060 line:80%
Those snow mountains are far away.

00:05:16.940 --> 00:05:18.940 line:80%
How could I travel back and forth
in half a month?

00:05:22.700 --> 00:05:23.900 line:80%
Now that the crisis has passed,

00:05:24.140 --> 00:05:26.180 line:80%
you should rest and recover.

00:05:27.100 --> 00:05:28.660 line:80%
I asked my mother about the treasure

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:30.140 line:80%
that can cure Nether Aura.

00:05:30.420 --> 00:05:31.573 line:80%
She couldn't remember clearly

00:05:31.780 --> 00:05:33.220 line:80%
and said she needs to look again

00:05:33.340 --> 00:05:35.173 line:80%
through the notes and letters
left by my aunt.

00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:38.140 line:80%
My mother

00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:40.340 line:80%
and my grandfather owe Luoying Valley.

00:05:40.860 --> 00:05:42.260 line:80%
Yet you're still willing to help me.

00:05:43.260 --> 00:05:44.420 line:80%
I'm deeply grateful.

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:49.740 line:80%
If you truly feel sorry,

00:05:50.220 --> 00:05:51.060 line:80%
why not pick

00:05:51.460 --> 00:05:53.060 line:80%
a few treasures from Guangtian Sect

00:05:54.660 --> 00:05:56.140 line:80%
and give them to me?

00:05:59.020 --> 00:06:00.780 line:80%
You can have anything

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:02.380 line:80%
that Guangtian Sect and I have.

00:06:04.020 --> 00:06:05.660 line:80%
Thank you in advance.

00:06:08.060 --> 00:06:08.900 line:80%
This money

00:06:09.100 --> 00:06:11.140 line:80%
is enough for you to open several shops.

00:06:14.180 --> 00:06:15.093 line:80%
Where did it come from?

00:06:15.900 --> 00:06:17.100 line:80%
Zhao, you've struck it rich.

00:06:17.260 --> 00:06:18.500 line:80%
Yuzhi's payment to me.

00:06:19.380 --> 00:06:20.540 line:80%
The saliva is expensive.

00:06:21.046 --> 00:06:22.449 line:80%
Does that mean Yuzhi's cultivation

00:06:22.460 --> 00:06:24.460 line:80%
can recover with the saliva?

00:06:24.820 --> 00:06:25.940 line:80%
He's not fully recovered,

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:27.420 line:80%
but he's been better.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.169 line:80%
If he wants a complete cure,

00:06:29.180 --> 00:06:30.580 line:80%
he'll still need a healing treasure.

00:06:32.020 --> 00:06:33.420 line:80%
Heaven truly envies talent.

00:06:33.780 --> 00:06:36.140 line:80%
Uncle said Chang's poison
has also not been fully cured

00:06:36.380 --> 00:06:37.930 line:80%
and still needs an antidote.

00:06:41.860 --> 00:06:43.700 line:80%
Take out the remaining saliva.

00:06:43.966 --> 00:06:45.653 line:80%
- My wounds haven't healed.
- Take it out.

00:06:45.666 --> 00:06:47.133 line:80%
- I can't win.
- Take out the saliva.

00:06:47.460 --> 00:06:49.100 line:80%
You soaked in the Wanzai Hot Spring

00:06:49.140 --> 00:06:49.980 line:80%
for quite some time.

00:06:50.060 --> 00:06:51.100 line:80%
Your injuries have healed.

00:06:51.300 --> 00:06:53.180 line:80%
Only one of his poisons
remains hard to remove.

00:06:53.340 --> 00:06:54.320 line:80%
So, he still needs rest.

00:06:55.820 --> 00:06:56.660 line:80%
Zhao,

00:06:57.100 --> 00:06:58.780 line:80%
that day at the Dusk Palace,

00:06:58.860 --> 00:07:01.100 line:80%
you accused Ning
of being a demonic sect spy.

00:07:01.100 --> 00:07:01.940 line:80%
Was that true?

00:07:02.020 --> 00:07:02.980 line:80%
Of course not.

00:07:03.420 --> 00:07:04.346 line:80%
That was just for show.

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:06.060 line:80%
Otherwise, how could we

00:07:06.300 --> 00:07:07.396 line:80%
draw them out

00:07:07.407 --> 00:07:08.647 line:80%
and expose the Body Shift plot?

00:07:10.020 --> 00:07:11.220 line:80%
That's what I thought.

00:07:11.580 --> 00:07:13.220 line:80%
Chang's acting was so convincing.

00:07:14.100 --> 00:07:16.500 line:80%
That reaction had me thinking
he truly fled in fear of guilt.

00:07:17.740 --> 00:07:19.860 line:80%
Then where is Ning now?

00:07:21.100 --> 00:07:22.060 line:80%
Who knows?

00:07:22.353 --> 00:07:24.180 line:80%
Maybe he's hiding somewhere
enjoying himself.

00:07:24.180 --> 00:07:25.180 line:80%
Now that he's healed,

00:07:26.333 --> 00:07:27.979 line:80%
he's probably making
a fortune somewhere.

00:07:28.220 --> 00:07:29.660 line:80%
Anyway, he never wanted to stay here.

00:07:31.140 --> 00:07:32.900 line:80%
Didn't he swear
to avenge his father before?

00:07:33.060 --> 00:07:34.540 line:80%
People change.

00:07:35.460 --> 00:07:37.660 line:80%
He might've made another decision.

00:07:47.460 --> 00:07:50.420 line:80%
(Li Sect, Youming Path)

00:08:15.518 --> 00:08:16.898 line:80%
(Yu Huiyin, Strategist of Li Sect)

00:08:16.909 --> 00:08:17.622 line:80%
Young...

00:08:18.300 --> 00:08:19.140 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:08:19.460 --> 00:08:20.540 line:80%
you're still alive.

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:23.340 line:80%
A mere injury from the Wudu Palm.

00:08:23.860 --> 00:08:24.860 line:80%
What's so hard to cure?

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:27.940 line:80%
Go back and tell Nie Zhe

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:30.040 line:80%
that the Young Master is back

00:08:30.260 --> 00:08:31.860 line:80%
and will reclaim everything that belongs

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:32.980 line:80%
to the Mu clan.

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:55.420 line:80%
♪Green robes, oh green robes♪

00:08:55.460 --> 00:08:58.660 line:80%
♪Green on the outside, yellow within♪

00:08:58.980 --> 00:09:02.300 line:80%
♪The sorrow in my heart♪

00:09:02.540 --> 00:09:09.380 line:80%
♪When will it ever end♪

00:09:38.660 --> 00:09:40.300 line:80%
You've always been meticulous

00:09:40.340 --> 00:09:41.500 line:80%
and steady in your actions.

00:09:42.460 --> 00:09:45.300 line:80%
How could this brilliant scheme
to topple Qingque Sect

00:09:46.140 --> 00:09:47.460 line:80%
have failed?

00:09:48.100 --> 00:09:48.940 line:80%
Originally,

00:09:49.180 --> 00:09:50.900 line:80%
everything was under my control.

00:09:51.140 --> 00:09:52.740 line:80%
However, Cai Pingshu's niece

00:09:52.980 --> 00:09:55.020 line:80%
obtained the antidote to the Body Shift.

00:09:55.740 --> 00:09:57.780 line:80%
Thus, the plan failed.

00:09:59.780 --> 00:10:01.340 line:80%
Cai Pingshu's niece?

00:10:02.220 --> 00:10:03.380 line:80%
How is her martial skill?

00:10:03.580 --> 00:10:05.780 line:80%
She bears much
of Cai Pingshu's former presence.

00:10:06.780 --> 00:10:09.580 line:80%
I never expected Cai Pingshu
to leave behind such a remnant

00:10:09.980 --> 00:10:11.820 line:80%
to continue wreaking havoc on our sect.

00:10:21.380 --> 00:10:22.900 line:80%
Chief...

00:10:38.460 --> 00:10:40.940 line:80%
(Sun Ruoshui, Li Sect)

00:10:42.620 --> 00:10:43.460 line:80%
Chief.

00:10:43.620 --> 00:10:44.460 line:80%
Do you know

00:10:44.780 --> 00:10:46.460 line:80%
your son has returned?

00:10:48.380 --> 00:10:49.220 line:80%
Impossible.

00:10:52.420 --> 00:10:53.740 line:80%
He's back,

00:10:54.620 --> 00:10:57.420 line:80%
unaffected by your poison.

00:10:57.580 --> 00:10:58.420 line:80%
Impossible.

00:10:58.500 --> 00:10:59.740 line:80%
Chief, you must believe me.

00:10:59.740 --> 00:11:00.820 line:80%
This poison has no cure.

00:11:01.460 --> 00:11:02.300 line:80%
Mu...

00:11:05.060 --> 00:11:05.900 line:80%
He is

00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:07.540 line:80%
just struggling to live.

00:11:07.740 --> 00:11:09.180 line:80%
He'll die soon.

00:11:12.860 --> 00:11:14.260 line:80%
Of course, I believe you.

00:11:15.620 --> 00:11:17.060 line:80%
But isn't this too coincidental?

00:11:18.380 --> 00:11:19.980 line:80%
He appeared

00:11:20.580 --> 00:11:22.220 line:80%
precisely when the strategist

00:11:22.420 --> 00:11:23.620 line:80%
screwed up the plan.

00:11:34.180 --> 00:11:35.860 line:80%
Where did Chang Ning of Chang Fort go?

00:11:36.420 --> 00:11:37.980 line:80%
Why is there not the slightest clue

00:11:38.107 --> 00:11:39.413 line:80%
about the item we're looking for?

00:11:39.424 --> 00:11:41.020 line:80%
After Chang Ning went down the mountain,

00:11:41.031 --> 00:11:42.133 line:80%
he vanished without a trace.

00:11:42.420 --> 00:11:44.700 line:80%
I've sent people to search everywhere.

00:11:44.900 --> 00:11:46.660 line:80%
Make sure to find that item.

00:11:46.740 --> 00:11:47.860 line:80%
Understood.

00:11:49.020 --> 00:11:51.140 line:80%
Time to think about how to deal
with Mu Qingyan.

00:11:54.580 --> 00:11:55.540 line:80%
Elder Hufa,

00:11:56.100 --> 00:11:56.940 line:80%
what do you think?

00:12:04.740 --> 00:12:07.540 line:80%
(Hu Fengge, Elder Hufa of Li Sect)

00:12:08.140 --> 00:12:09.260 line:80%
Rest assured, Chief.

00:12:10.580 --> 00:12:11.420 line:80%
Once he comes,

00:12:12.180 --> 00:12:13.020 line:80%
he will surely die.

00:12:13.660 --> 00:12:14.860 line:80%
With you and the strategist,

00:12:15.820 --> 00:12:17.380 line:80%
I naturally feel at ease.

00:12:36.700 --> 00:12:37.900 line:80%
Cai Pingshu's niece

00:12:38.300 --> 00:12:39.540 line:80%
has such courage.

00:12:40.580 --> 00:12:41.940 line:80%
I was careless and got struck

00:12:43.100 --> 00:12:44.860 line:80%
by Qi Yunke's Huolong Palm.

00:12:47.027 --> 00:12:48.227 line:80%
Had I known this would happen,

00:12:48.820 --> 00:12:49.980 line:80%
I should've gone with you.

00:12:53.700 --> 00:12:55.220 line:80%
If you didn't stay in Bliss Palace,

00:12:56.340 --> 00:12:57.180 line:80%
how could I

00:12:58.460 --> 00:12:59.780 line:80%
be at ease outside?

00:13:03.460 --> 00:13:04.940 line:80%
Mu Qingyan has returned

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:07.740 line:80%
with better martial strength.

00:13:09.420 --> 00:13:10.260 line:80%
Maybe

00:13:10.620 --> 00:13:12.260 line:80%
he cultivated some miraculous method.

00:13:13.700 --> 00:13:14.540 line:80%
Moreover,

00:13:14.980 --> 00:13:15.980 line:80%
Qinong's token has fallen

00:13:16.700 --> 00:13:19.020 line:80%
into Cai Pingshu's niece's hands.

00:13:19.580 --> 00:13:20.420 line:80%
I fear

00:13:20.740 --> 00:13:22.340 line:80%
Qinong and Elder Tianji

00:13:24.500 --> 00:13:25.700 line:80%
are already dead.

00:13:26.660 --> 00:13:27.986 line:80%
With troubles within and without,

00:13:28.340 --> 00:13:29.380 line:80%
in these turbulent times,

00:13:30.420 --> 00:13:31.260 line:80%
you and I

00:13:33.100 --> 00:13:34.860 line:80%
must not be careless.

00:13:44.266 --> 00:13:46.415 line:80%
(To Zhao, my daughter)
Yuzhi, my mother has replied.

00:13:46.540 --> 00:13:48.620 line:80%
This treasure is called Jade Sunflower.

00:13:48.780 --> 00:13:50.820 line:80%
It was stolen
from the demonic sect's treasury

00:13:50.820 --> 00:13:51.840 line:80%
by my aunt's close friend.

00:13:51.940 --> 00:13:54.100 line:80%
After curing
the Shi brothers' Nether Aura,

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:55.773 line:80%
its whereabouts became unknown.

00:13:56.140 --> 00:13:56.980 line:80%
So,

00:13:57.860 --> 00:13:58.900 line:80%
there is still no clue.

00:13:59.460 --> 00:14:00.300 line:80%
I suspect

00:14:00.659 --> 00:14:02.420 line:80%
it returned
to the demonic sect's treasury.

00:14:02.500 --> 00:14:03.340 line:80%
How do you know?

00:14:03.860 --> 00:14:05.340 line:80%
My aunt acted with integrity.

00:14:05.500 --> 00:14:06.353 line:80%
She wouldn't keep

00:14:06.364 --> 00:14:07.820 line:80%
a demonic sect treasure for herself.

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:10.340 line:80%
I think after using the Jade Sunflower,

00:14:10.900 --> 00:14:12.020 line:80%
she returned it intact.

00:14:12.340 --> 00:14:13.860 line:80%
Ms. Cai truly was such a person.

00:14:17.100 --> 00:14:19.060 line:80%
Why don't we go steal it

00:14:19.260 --> 00:14:20.940 line:80%
from the demonic sect treasury?

00:14:21.060 --> 00:14:22.780 line:80%
The demonic sect is in great turmoil.

00:14:22.980 --> 00:14:23.820 line:80%
It's not that simple.

00:14:24.140 --> 00:14:25.060 line:80%
What are you two doing?

00:14:28.340 --> 00:14:29.300 line:80%
What are you two doing?

00:14:30.180 --> 00:14:31.780 line:80%
We're discussing important matters.

00:14:31.980 --> 00:14:34.173 line:80%
What important matter
requires discussing face-to-face?

00:14:34.500 --> 00:14:35.700 line:80%
- Lingbo, I...
- Quiet.

00:14:35.740 --> 00:14:36.580 line:80%
I wasn't asking you.

00:14:38.460 --> 00:14:39.420 line:80%
I can't tell you now.

00:14:39.500 --> 00:14:40.500 line:80%
Even to me?

00:14:41.260 --> 00:14:42.340 line:80%
But you can tell her?

00:14:43.140 --> 00:14:44.180 line:80%
Lingbo, actually...

00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:45.213 line:80%
No need to explain to her.

00:14:46.340 --> 00:14:47.180 line:80%
Qi Lingbo,

00:14:47.740 --> 00:14:49.220 line:80%
have you already forgotten

00:14:49.231 --> 00:14:50.460 line:80%
what you said to me days ago?

00:14:54.660 --> 00:14:55.500 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:14:56.500 --> 00:14:58.140 line:80%
do you think I'm too stupid

00:14:58.740 --> 00:15:00.780 line:80%
and incompetent to help you?

00:15:01.500 --> 00:15:03.260 line:80%
Is that why you discuss
everything with her?

00:15:03.500 --> 00:15:04.820 line:80%
Or is it you...

00:15:04.820 --> 00:15:05.753 line:80%
You're overthinking it.

00:15:06.300 --> 00:15:07.140 line:80%
I'm not.

00:15:08.020 --> 00:15:09.860 line:80%
I'm the one closest to you.

00:15:10.940 --> 00:15:12.300 line:80%
Yet now, you're not even willing

00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:13.900 line:80%
to talk to me.

00:15:16.100 --> 00:15:16.940 line:80%
Well,

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:19.260 line:80%
sorry to interrupt you two.

00:15:20.353 --> 00:15:21.340 line:80%
I'll take my leave first.

00:15:22.500 --> 00:15:23.820 line:80%
Cai Zhao, stop right there.

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:24.940 line:80%
Cai Zhao, stop right there!

00:15:26.300 --> 00:15:27.140 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:15:29.780 --> 00:15:30.620 line:80%
Father.

00:15:30.660 --> 00:15:31.500 line:80%
Uncle.

00:15:34.460 --> 00:15:35.300 line:80%
You're bleeding.

00:15:45.300 --> 00:15:46.140 line:80%
Son,

00:15:46.520 --> 00:15:47.555 line:80%
didn't you use to dislike

00:15:47.566 --> 00:15:49.300 line:80%
these gold and silver vulgarities
the most?

00:15:49.500 --> 00:15:51.780 line:80%
Why have people deliver these this time?

00:15:52.300 --> 00:15:53.260 line:80%
Zhao likes them.

00:15:53.539 --> 00:15:54.620 line:80%
Compared to refined objects,

00:15:54.940 --> 00:15:56.380 line:80%
she seems to prefer gold and silver.

00:15:58.700 --> 00:16:00.300 line:80%
These are for Zhao?

00:16:04.100 --> 00:16:05.220 line:80%
You like her.

00:16:07.300 --> 00:16:08.140 line:80%
I'm giving her these

00:16:08.505 --> 00:16:10.226 line:80%
to thank her for helping me
find medicine.

00:16:10.926 --> 00:16:12.180 line:80%
I'm still bound by a betrothal.

00:16:12.860 --> 00:16:14.033 line:80%
Father, please don't say that.

00:16:14.140 --> 00:16:15.500 line:80%
Don't harm Zhao's reputation.

00:16:15.940 --> 00:16:16.820 line:80%
Son,

00:16:16.860 --> 00:16:17.740 line:80%
listen to me.

00:16:18.300 --> 00:16:20.540 line:80%
A true confidant is hard to find.

00:16:21.540 --> 00:16:23.980 line:80%
Fate is something you must seize.

00:16:24.780 --> 00:16:25.620 line:80%
To be honest,

00:16:25.780 --> 00:16:27.100 line:80%
your betrothal to Lingbo

00:16:27.140 --> 00:16:29.780 line:80%
was decided on a whim
by your mother and Lady Yin.

00:16:29.791 --> 00:16:31.345 line:80%
I've always felt it was inappropriate.

00:16:31.460 --> 00:16:32.300 line:80%
Coincidentally,

00:16:32.380 --> 00:16:34.460 line:80%
Lady Yin invited me to discuss matters.

00:16:34.980 --> 00:16:36.620 line:80%
I can just help you annul the betrothal.

00:16:36.900 --> 00:16:37.740 line:80%
Father,

00:16:37.940 --> 00:16:38.980 line:80%
a betrothal is serious.

00:16:40.060 --> 00:16:42.580 line:80%
Even if I have no feelings for Lingbo,

00:16:42.593 --> 00:16:43.973 line:80%
I must first report this to Master.

00:16:44.820 --> 00:16:45.660 line:80%
Moreover,

00:16:45.886 --> 00:16:47.520 line:80%
the sect's turmoil
has only just settled,

00:16:48.100 --> 00:16:49.540 line:80%
and Senior Qiu just died.

00:16:50.286 --> 00:16:51.660 line:80%
If we break off the betrothal now,

00:16:51.740 --> 00:16:53.613 line:80%
everyone will think Lingbo despises me

00:16:53.624 --> 00:16:54.810 line:80%
for being injured and useless.

00:16:55.420 --> 00:16:57.340 line:80%
How would Lingbo
face herself in the future?

00:16:58.700 --> 00:16:59.540 line:80%
Son,

00:16:59.660 --> 00:17:01.740 line:80%
you always hesitate like this.

00:17:02.420 --> 00:17:03.940 line:80%
What if Zhao leaves you?

00:17:05.100 --> 00:17:06.260 line:80%
I still need to cultivate.

00:17:07.060 --> 00:17:07.900 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:17:08.100 --> 00:17:08.940 line:80%
You...

00:17:18.060 --> 00:17:19.660 line:80%
Look, the fish have grown quite a bit.

00:17:19.780 --> 00:17:20.620 line:80%
Feed them some more.

00:17:22.300 --> 00:17:23.140 line:80%
Look at that one.

00:17:23.940 --> 00:17:26.780 line:80%
I heard Yuzhi sent
a lot of valuables to Zhao.

00:17:26.900 --> 00:17:28.100 line:80%
Shijun, do you know about it?

00:17:29.300 --> 00:17:30.820 line:80%
The saliva Zhao sent over

00:17:30.820 --> 00:17:32.380 line:80%
is truly good stuff.

00:17:32.460 --> 00:17:33.700 line:80%
Yuzhi used it in his medicine,

00:17:33.780 --> 00:17:35.740 line:80%
and the cold energy
in his body decreased a lot.

00:17:35.780 --> 00:17:36.660 line:80%
With such great merit,

00:17:37.020 --> 00:17:38.500 line:80%
even sending more treasures

00:17:38.620 --> 00:17:39.700 line:80%
would be only proper.

00:17:41.740 --> 00:17:44.100 line:80%
Zhao did a great service this time.

00:17:46.300 --> 00:17:47.260 line:80%
Back then,

00:17:47.420 --> 00:17:48.780 line:80%
Pingshu's grace and bearing

00:17:48.900 --> 00:17:50.300 line:80%
were already breathtaking.

00:17:51.020 --> 00:17:53.460 line:80%
What a surprise that her niece
would be just as outstanding.

00:17:53.940 --> 00:17:54.940 line:80%
So young,

00:17:55.093 --> 00:17:56.393 line:80%
yet calm in the face of trouble,

00:17:56.620 --> 00:17:57.500 line:80%
brave and resourceful,

00:17:57.700 --> 00:17:58.966 line:80%
worthy of great responsibility.

00:17:59.180 --> 00:18:01.940 line:80%
The Cais did a great job in parenting.

00:18:03.260 --> 00:18:05.700 line:80%
Yuzhi also showed
the air of a great general.

00:18:05.900 --> 00:18:07.260 line:80%
If not for his steady response,

00:18:07.620 --> 00:18:09.820 line:80%
there might've been complications.

00:18:10.260 --> 00:18:11.780 line:80%
Shijun, have some tea.

00:18:16.380 --> 00:18:19.060 line:80%
Yuzhi naturally carries
my old style and spirit.

00:18:24.780 --> 00:18:26.580 line:80%
I only hate the Nether Aura.

00:18:27.340 --> 00:18:28.380 line:80%
Once I leave,

00:18:28.740 --> 00:18:30.180 line:80%
even if I wear out iron shoes

00:18:30.299 --> 00:18:31.333 line:80%
and spend all my wealth,

00:18:31.344 --> 00:18:33.233 line:80%
I'll try my best to find
more medicine for him.

00:18:33.740 --> 00:18:34.780 line:80%
Are you going to leave?

00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:36.340 line:80%
Yes.

00:18:36.500 --> 00:18:38.220 line:80%
There are many matters in the sect,

00:18:38.380 --> 00:18:39.940 line:80%
all borne by Xiuzhi alone.

00:18:39.940 --> 00:18:41.340 line:80%
I can't set my mind at ease.

00:18:42.060 --> 00:18:43.180 line:80%
Since you're about to leave,

00:18:43.180 --> 00:18:44.460 line:80%
why not take these two days

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:47.700 line:80%
to set Lingbo and Yuzhi's wedding date?

00:18:48.020 --> 00:18:50.660 line:80%
It will also make it easier for Lingbo
to take care of Yuzhi.

00:18:52.300 --> 00:18:53.140 line:80%
Well.

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:55.060 line:80%
There's no rush.

00:18:55.100 --> 00:18:55.940 line:80%
No rush.

00:18:57.420 --> 00:18:58.980 line:80%
Let's wait until Yuzhi recovers.

00:18:59.260 --> 00:19:00.980 line:80%
What if his injury never heals?

00:19:03.380 --> 00:19:04.820 line:80%
Yuzhi is still young.

00:19:05.140 --> 00:19:06.100 line:80%
One year, two years,

00:19:06.300 --> 00:19:07.500 line:80%
at most three or five years.

00:19:07.500 --> 00:19:08.740 line:80%
He will recover eventually.

00:19:09.260 --> 00:19:10.100 line:80%
As for the marriage,

00:19:10.540 --> 00:19:11.580 line:80%
we can decide later.

00:19:44.940 --> 00:19:45.780 line:80%
Let me see.

00:19:49.420 --> 00:19:50.420 line:80%
Milady,

00:19:50.820 --> 00:19:52.060 line:80%
you don't need to do

00:19:52.340 --> 00:19:54.620 line:80%
such rough work.

00:19:55.180 --> 00:19:57.020 line:80%
Just have the servants do it.

00:19:58.180 --> 00:19:59.260 line:80%
No.

00:19:59.580 --> 00:20:01.420 line:80%
This is something close to Yuzhi.

00:20:01.860 --> 00:20:03.260 line:80%
How could I let others handle it?

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:05.000 line:80%
It's getting cold.

00:20:05.260 --> 00:20:06.820 line:80%
I need to finish it quickly for Yuzhi.

00:20:06.980 --> 00:20:08.580 line:80%
No need to care so much about him.

00:20:14.020 --> 00:20:15.740 line:80%
Yuzhi is my fiancé.

00:20:16.060 --> 00:20:17.460 line:80%
If I don't care, who will?

00:20:17.660 --> 00:20:19.660 line:80%
But what if he doesn't have you
in his heart?

00:20:22.380 --> 00:20:24.260 line:80%
Yuzhi and I grew up together.

00:20:24.363 --> 00:20:25.832 line:80%
How could he not have me in his heart?

00:20:26.260 --> 00:20:27.860 line:80%
It's just that he's been injured lately,

00:20:27.860 --> 00:20:28.900 line:80%
and his mood is low.

00:20:29.460 --> 00:20:31.060 line:80%
He is a bit more distant than before.

00:20:32.060 --> 00:20:33.140 line:80%
But in the end,

00:20:33.300 --> 00:20:34.500 line:80%
we do have a betrothal.

00:20:34.860 --> 00:20:36.620 line:80%
The betrothal was decided by the elders.

00:20:36.767 --> 00:20:37.940 line:80%
It's not impossible to cancel.

00:20:39.660 --> 00:20:40.500 line:80%
Mother,

00:20:42.740 --> 00:20:44.940 line:80%
the betrothal was decided
by you and Aunt.

00:20:45.306 --> 00:20:47.300 line:80%
Before Aunt passed away,
she repeatedly instructed

00:20:47.340 --> 00:20:48.793 line:80%
that this betrothal must be honored.

00:20:48.900 --> 00:20:50.206 line:80%
How could we go back on our word?

00:20:50.540 --> 00:20:52.100 line:80%
I made a mistake.

00:20:52.540 --> 00:20:54.020 line:80%
Your aunt passed away so suddenly.

00:20:54.100 --> 00:20:55.420 line:80%
That's why it was decided hastily.

00:20:56.060 --> 00:20:57.900 line:80%
You know Yuzhi better than anyone.

00:20:58.100 --> 00:20:59.740 line:80%
He only loves martial cultivation.

00:20:59.846 --> 00:21:00.820 line:80%
His temperament is cold.

00:21:01.180 --> 00:21:02.420 line:80%
He's not close to you.

00:21:03.420 --> 00:21:04.260 line:80%
So,

00:21:04.580 --> 00:21:06.126 line:80%
you told me to restrain my temperament

00:21:06.180 --> 00:21:07.540 line:80%
and get closer to Yuzhi.

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:09.260 line:80%
After Yuzhi was injured,

00:21:09.271 --> 00:21:10.602 line:80%
I showed care and consideration,

00:21:10.613 --> 00:21:11.533 line:80%
attentive in every way.

00:21:11.820 --> 00:21:13.180 line:80%
I've done all of that.

00:21:14.300 --> 00:21:15.620 line:80%
But however you please him,

00:21:16.180 --> 00:21:17.980 line:80%
has he ever been even gentler
toward you?

00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:22.260 line:80%
I can't bear to see you suffer anymore.

00:21:22.660 --> 00:21:23.500 line:80%
From now on,

00:21:23.740 --> 00:21:24.940 line:80%
keep some distance from him.

00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:28.340 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:21:28.980 --> 00:21:30.140 line:80%
I don't think I'm suffering.

00:21:31.260 --> 00:21:32.100 line:80%
Very soon,

00:21:32.260 --> 00:21:33.620 line:80%
Yuzhi's injury will heal,

00:21:34.100 --> 00:21:35.780 line:80%
and everything will get better.

00:21:35.780 --> 00:21:37.020 line:80%
Stop deceiving yourself.

00:21:37.500 --> 00:21:39.500 line:80%
The poison he suffered is Nether Aura.

00:21:39.780 --> 00:21:41.460 line:80%
The chance of recovery is slim.

00:21:41.780 --> 00:21:43.620 line:80%
He may never be the Lord.

00:21:44.100 --> 00:21:45.540 line:80%
And you are the Lord's daughter.

00:21:45.700 --> 00:21:47.620 line:80%
If your husband
can't love you or protect you,

00:21:47.820 --> 00:21:50.060 line:80%
how will you secure
your position in the sect?

00:21:50.660 --> 00:21:51.780 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:21:52.460 --> 00:21:53.500 line:80%
Do you want me to abandon

00:21:53.511 --> 00:21:55.111 line:80%
my fiancé because of his incompetence

00:21:55.122 --> 00:21:56.540 line:80%
and marry another man just like you?

00:21:56.540 --> 00:21:57.380 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:21:57.540 --> 00:21:59.500 line:80%
Everything I do is for your own good.

00:21:59.766 --> 00:22:01.980 line:80%
The Yins have operated
within the sect for generations.

00:22:01.980 --> 00:22:03.680 line:80%
Are we to watch helplessly
as someone else

00:22:03.700 --> 00:22:05.060 line:80%
takes charge of the sect?

00:22:05.060 --> 00:22:05.940 line:80%
So what?

00:22:06.340 --> 00:22:07.460 line:80%
What do you take me for?

00:22:07.940 --> 00:22:09.500 line:80%
A puppet to maintain the Yins' power?

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:11.780 line:80%
Enough. How dare you accuse me?

00:22:19.540 --> 00:22:21.060 line:80%
When I was lazy in cultivation before,

00:22:22.140 --> 00:22:24.140 line:80%
you failed to urge me to improve

00:22:24.660 --> 00:22:26.820 line:80%
and even told me stories
of powerful women

00:22:27.100 --> 00:22:28.500 line:80%
meeting tragic ends.

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:30.460 line:80%
But now,

00:22:30.900 --> 00:22:32.580 line:80%
I truly envy Cai Zhao.

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:34.860 line:80%
When the sect faced a crisis,

00:22:34.940 --> 00:22:36.020 line:80%
she was brave and fearless,

00:22:36.340 --> 00:22:37.660 line:80%
able to turn the tide.

00:22:37.940 --> 00:22:40.220 line:80%
She can do what she wants to do.

00:22:40.313 --> 00:22:42.369 line:80%
She doesn't need others
to love her or protect her.

00:22:42.380 --> 00:22:44.020 line:80%
She can protect herself.

00:22:45.700 --> 00:22:46.540 line:80%
Milady,

00:22:47.300 --> 00:22:48.980 line:80%
Lady Yin is only worried about you.

00:22:49.460 --> 00:22:50.860 line:80%
Is she worried about me,

00:22:50.940 --> 00:22:52.820 line:80%
or does she look down on me?

00:22:53.540 --> 00:22:55.260 line:80%
You were just like Grandfather,

00:22:55.260 --> 00:22:57.820 line:80%
believing women cannot be lords,

00:22:58.260 --> 00:22:59.980 line:80%
insisting on finding
a powerful husband,

00:23:00.340 --> 00:23:02.220 line:80%
until you met Cai Pingshu.

00:23:02.420 --> 00:23:03.453 line:80%
Then you finally realized

00:23:03.660 --> 00:23:05.540 line:80%
that women too can be powerful,

00:23:05.980 --> 00:23:07.860 line:80%
brave, and unstoppable.

00:23:10.300 --> 00:23:12.700 line:80%
So, you and Aunt harbored resentment,

00:23:13.220 --> 00:23:14.820 line:80%
targeting the Cais at every turn,

00:23:14.900 --> 00:23:17.340 line:80%
even using Cai Pingshu's tragic death
to warn me,

00:23:17.580 --> 00:23:18.989 line:80%
wanting me to walk the same path

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:20.540 line:80%
of attaching myself to others as you.

00:23:20.540 --> 00:23:21.882 line:80%
What's so great about Cai Pingshu?

00:23:21.893 --> 00:23:23.226 line:80%
She died young.

00:23:23.380 --> 00:23:25.900 line:80%
If I could die as spectacularly
as Cai Pingshu,

00:23:25.900 --> 00:23:27.220 line:80%
an early death would be worth it.

00:23:31.980 --> 00:23:32.820 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:23:33.820 --> 00:23:35.420 line:80%
What did I say wrong?

00:23:36.140 --> 00:23:38.260 line:80%
It was all Grandfather's selfishness

00:23:38.580 --> 00:23:40.700 line:80%
that caused so many tragedies
and disasters.

00:23:40.980 --> 00:23:42.380 line:80%
For the Yin's power,

00:23:42.460 --> 00:23:43.900 line:80%
for the position of the Lord's wife,

00:23:44.020 --> 00:23:45.940 line:80%
how many more people must you sacrifice?

00:23:48.100 --> 00:23:48.940 line:80%
Lingbo...

00:23:51.060 --> 00:23:51.900 line:80%
Milady.

00:23:52.780 --> 00:23:53.620 line:80%
Lingbo?

00:23:54.260 --> 00:23:55.100 line:80%
Milady.

00:23:57.060 --> 00:23:57.900 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:24:01.900 --> 00:24:03.220 line:80%
Dalou, why are you here?

00:24:04.260 --> 00:24:06.940 line:80%
I heard you were struck
by the Chaos Needle.

00:24:07.260 --> 00:24:09.740 line:80%
Why aren't you resting?

00:24:10.220 --> 00:24:11.340 line:80%
Thank you for your concern.

00:24:12.060 --> 00:24:13.260 line:80%
I'm already much better.

00:24:14.300 --> 00:24:15.380 line:80%
Master ordered me to come

00:24:16.100 --> 00:24:18.260 line:80%
and return this to you.

00:24:31.220 --> 00:24:32.660 line:80%
The Clearing Pill.

00:25:26.260 --> 00:25:30.420 line:80%
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

00:25:46.860 --> 00:25:47.940 line:80%
Since you're here,

00:25:48.780 --> 00:25:50.060 line:80%
come pay your respects.

00:25:54.340 --> 00:25:56.620 line:80%
Why did you have Dalou return the pill,

00:25:56.766 --> 00:25:57.906 line:80%
yet you didn't come yourself?

00:26:00.020 --> 00:26:00.940 line:80%
Since that day,

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:02.980 line:80%
you've been avoiding me.

00:26:03.500 --> 00:26:05.980 line:80%
Are you bothered by my past with Qiu?

00:26:07.186 --> 00:26:08.900 line:80%
When he pretended to be you,
we did not...

00:26:08.900 --> 00:26:10.780 line:80%
I know you did not cross any boundaries.

00:26:11.140 --> 00:26:12.580 line:80%
Then why is it?

00:26:13.100 --> 00:26:15.020 line:80%
Qiu held deep resentment
toward my father.

00:26:15.340 --> 00:26:16.620 line:80%
He left the sect long ago.

00:26:16.659 --> 00:26:17.980 line:80%
One-sided words cannot be trusted.

00:26:17.980 --> 00:26:18.820 line:80%
Dear,

00:26:19.580 --> 00:26:21.060 line:80%
even if Qiu Renjie wronged everyone,

00:26:21.060 --> 00:26:22.540 line:80%
he'd never wrong you.

00:26:23.700 --> 00:26:25.460 line:80%
If he truly intended to humiliate you,

00:26:25.460 --> 00:26:26.700 line:80%
he would not have repeatedly

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:28.140 line:80%
kept you outside his door.

00:26:29.540 --> 00:26:30.860 line:80%
If he truly were a spy,

00:26:31.220 --> 00:26:32.060 line:80%
even for appearances,

00:26:32.180 --> 00:26:33.900 line:80%
he would've pretended
to be close to you.

00:26:34.860 --> 00:26:36.420 line:80%
But he refused to approach you at all,

00:26:37.500 --> 00:26:38.860 line:80%
just to protect your reputation.

00:26:38.860 --> 00:26:40.620 line:80%
That was what let Yuzhi see the flaw.

00:26:42.540 --> 00:26:43.380 line:80%
Not to mention

00:26:44.060 --> 00:26:45.220 line:80%
that Clearing Pill.

00:26:47.020 --> 00:26:48.180 line:80%
Are you blaming me

00:26:48.340 --> 00:26:49.980 line:80%
for keeping the pill all these years?

00:26:50.700 --> 00:26:52.500 line:80%
Then what about you,

00:26:52.500 --> 00:26:53.980 line:80%
going to Luoying Valley every year,

00:26:53.980 --> 00:26:55.180 line:80%
thinking of a bedridden woman?

00:27:12.180 --> 00:27:13.100 line:80%
Forget it.

00:27:31.460 --> 00:27:35.980 line:80%
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

00:27:40.740 --> 00:27:46.220 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:27:54.300 --> 00:27:57.140 line:80%
(Lian Shisan, Li Sect)

00:28:10.220 --> 00:28:14.420 line:80%
(You Guanyue, Master of Qinglong Altar)

00:28:16.260 --> 00:28:17.500 line:80%
Today is Master You's birthday.

00:28:17.940 --> 00:28:19.540 line:80%
There should surely be many guests,

00:28:19.820 --> 00:28:21.020 line:80%
lively and bustling.

00:28:24.060 --> 00:28:26.180 line:80%
Thank you all for coming...

00:28:27.780 --> 00:28:28.620 line:80%
Where is everyone?

00:28:30.013 --> 00:28:31.300 line:80%
Why isn't there a single person?

00:28:32.940 --> 00:28:33.933 line:80%
This is bad, Master You.

00:28:34.613 --> 00:28:36.660 line:80%
There are rumors
that you colluded with Mu Qingyan,

00:28:36.671 --> 00:28:38.342 line:80%
just like your adoptive father,
Elder Qiu,

00:28:38.353 --> 00:28:39.129 line:80%
intending to rebel.

00:28:39.140 --> 00:28:40.220 line:80%
To avoid suspicion,

00:28:40.500 --> 00:28:41.540 line:80%
no one dares to come.

00:28:41.660 --> 00:28:42.500 line:80%
What?

00:28:43.860 --> 00:28:44.700 line:80%
Me?

00:28:45.820 --> 00:28:46.940 line:80%
Rebel?

00:28:47.780 --> 00:28:49.100 line:80%
Isn't this slandering me?

00:28:49.100 --> 00:28:51.540 line:80%
This is more unjust
than snow falling in midsummer.

00:28:55.780 --> 00:28:56.620 line:80%
Shisan,

00:28:58.100 --> 00:28:58.980 line:80%
bring paper and ink.

00:28:59.620 --> 00:29:00.460 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:13.980 --> 00:29:16.420 line:80%
This petition of grievance to the Chief

00:29:17.380 --> 00:29:18.580 line:80%
must show some sincerity.

00:29:27.060 --> 00:29:27.900 line:80%
Shisan,

00:29:28.653 --> 00:29:30.060 line:80%
let me see your long, slender hand.

00:29:34.940 --> 00:29:35.780 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:29:41.940 --> 00:29:43.260 line:80%
Dear Chief,

00:29:43.580 --> 00:29:45.620 line:80%
since joining the Li Sect,

00:29:45.900 --> 00:29:49.300 line:80%
I've only known the Nie clan,
never the Mu clan.

00:29:52.540 --> 00:29:54.060 line:80%
My loyalty to you

00:29:55.020 --> 00:29:58.180 line:80%
is wholehearted and true.

00:30:02.980 --> 00:30:04.220 line:80%
It's Master You's birthday.

00:30:04.660 --> 00:30:06.500 line:80%
Why is it so desolate?

00:30:12.660 --> 00:30:14.140 line:80%
Mr. Yu, you're here.

00:30:14.660 --> 00:30:16.580 line:80%
My Qinglong Altar is truly honored.

00:30:16.900 --> 00:30:17.900 line:80%
I heard that you stirred

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:19.420 line:80%
the Six Sects into discord

00:30:19.860 --> 00:30:22.220 line:80%
and left them with a mess with ghostly

00:30:22.220 --> 00:30:23.260 line:80%
and unfathomable methods.

00:30:23.580 --> 00:30:26.100 line:80%
What a remarkable deed.

00:30:26.380 --> 00:30:27.900 line:80%
What have I done to deserve

00:30:28.780 --> 00:30:31.060 line:80%
your personal congratulations?

00:30:33.380 --> 00:30:34.220 line:80%
I...

00:30:34.340 --> 00:30:35.860 line:80%
I'm so moved that I could cry.

00:30:36.940 --> 00:30:37.780 line:80%
Li Yi.

00:30:39.340 --> 00:30:41.180 line:80%
The Chief heard it's your birthday

00:30:41.420 --> 00:30:43.100 line:80%
and had someone find

00:30:43.420 --> 00:30:45.740 line:80%
Elder Qiu's spear from the treasury

00:30:45.980 --> 00:30:47.260 line:80%
as a gift.

00:30:51.060 --> 00:30:52.820 line:80%
Master You, do not overthink it.

00:30:53.660 --> 00:30:54.980 line:80%
The Chief means

00:30:55.540 --> 00:30:57.260 line:80%
that Elder Qiu's position

00:30:57.580 --> 00:30:59.980 line:80%
will sooner or later be yours.

00:30:59.980 --> 00:31:01.540 line:80%
The Qinglong Altar guards the first line

00:31:01.540 --> 00:31:02.780 line:80%
of our Li Sect.

00:31:03.060 --> 00:31:05.660 line:80%
We will rely on you even more.

00:31:06.780 --> 00:31:08.780 line:80%
Thanks to the Chief.

00:31:09.460 --> 00:31:10.380 line:80%
Thanks, Mr. Yu.

00:31:10.780 --> 00:31:12.140 line:80%
My subordinate, Li Yi,

00:31:12.460 --> 00:31:14.820 line:80%
has long admired your talent.

00:31:15.300 --> 00:31:17.140 line:80%
Today, I'll do a small favor

00:31:17.140 --> 00:31:18.580 line:80%
and let him stay here

00:31:18.700 --> 00:31:20.900 line:80%
to seek guidance from you.

00:31:21.340 --> 00:31:23.060 line:80%
(Li Yi, Li Sect)
I long for your advice.

00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:29.460 line:80%
Master You is unwilling.

00:31:29.780 --> 00:31:30.620 line:80%
Then, let's go.

00:31:30.660 --> 00:31:31.780 line:80%
With Li's help,

00:31:32.060 --> 00:31:34.060 line:80%
we'll surely be like a tiger with wings.

00:31:34.380 --> 00:31:37.540 line:80%
I won't fail the trust
of Mr. Yu and the Chief.

00:31:44.300 --> 00:31:45.220 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:31:45.460 --> 00:31:46.340 line:80%
Guidance?

00:31:46.780 --> 00:31:48.180 line:80%
He's clearly here to spy on me.

00:31:49.860 --> 00:31:51.460 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

00:31:52.900 --> 00:31:53.740 line:80%
Father.

00:31:54.940 --> 00:31:55.900 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:32:00.260 --> 00:32:01.180 line:80%
Darn it.

00:32:02.460 --> 00:32:03.900 line:80%
Who wants to harm me?

00:32:11.540 --> 00:32:15.500 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang,
Elder Tianquan)

00:32:19.500 --> 00:32:20.340 line:80%
Father,

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:22.220 line:80%
you're magnanimous.

00:32:23.380 --> 00:32:24.420 line:80%
Don't blame me.

00:32:30.320 --> 00:32:31.210 line:80%
Who?

00:32:31.220 --> 00:32:32.060 line:80%
Who dares to hit me?

00:32:34.780 --> 00:32:36.180 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

00:32:43.780 --> 00:32:44.620 line:80%
Father,

00:32:45.620 --> 00:32:46.620 line:80%
don't harm me.

00:32:47.620 --> 00:32:48.500 line:80%
You're magnanimous.

00:32:58.820 --> 00:32:59.700 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet)

00:33:01.740 --> 00:33:02.620 line:80%
Father,

00:33:03.380 --> 00:33:04.860 line:80%
I know you died unjustly.

00:33:05.300 --> 00:33:07.100 line:80%
But my life in the sect
isn't easy either.

00:33:07.300 --> 00:33:08.140 line:80%
Every day,

00:33:08.700 --> 00:33:10.020 line:80%
danger lurks everywhere.

00:33:10.133 --> 00:33:11.286 line:80%
I'm like walking on thin ice.

00:33:11.460 --> 00:33:14.380 line:80%
I'm already 31 this year,

00:33:15.180 --> 00:33:16.500 line:80%
yet I still haven't married Xing.

00:33:16.580 --> 00:33:18.180 line:80%
You don't even have a grandson.

00:33:18.820 --> 00:33:20.180 line:80%
If you kill me,

00:33:20.780 --> 00:33:21.620 line:80%
there will be no one

00:33:23.180 --> 00:33:24.580 line:80%
left to worship you.

00:33:25.060 --> 00:33:26.740 line:80%
Father, you're magnanimous.

00:33:26.780 --> 00:33:27.620 line:80%
I'll kowtow to you.

00:33:37.780 --> 00:33:39.253 line:80%
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)
Rebel!

00:33:39.340 --> 00:33:40.180 line:80%
I...

00:33:42.380 --> 00:33:43.220 line:80%
Get lost!

00:33:44.340 --> 00:33:45.540 line:80%
What a jerk!

00:33:46.020 --> 00:33:46.860 line:80%
Go die!

00:33:48.380 --> 00:33:51.420 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:34:37.041 --> 00:34:47.701 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:35:06.461 --> 00:35:10.871 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:35:11.436 --> 00:35:16.051 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:35:16.391 --> 00:35:20.956 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:35:21.481 --> 00:35:25.781 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:35:28.726 --> 00:35:33.426 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:33.951 --> 00:35:38.241 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:35:38.901 --> 00:35:42.931 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:35:43.246 --> 00:35:48.371 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:35:48.946 --> 00:35:53.756 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:53.971 --> 00:35:58.141 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:35:58.866 --> 00:36:02.801 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:36:03.301 --> 00:36:08.576 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:36:31.306 --> 00:36:36.436 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:36.801 --> 00:36:41.171 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:36:41.436 --> 00:36:45.566 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:36:45.751 --> 00:36:51.326 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪